  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/2a7224d8e4bbc0969ce88c05fad2eb08.poster.avif?t=1742819123\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/2a7224d8e4bbc0969ce88c05fad2eb08.webm?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/2a7224d8e4bbc0969ce88c05fad2eb08.mp4?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OhShape is a rhythm VR game where players <strong>dance with their full body</strong> to go through, punch, and dodge walls following the beat of the music. Enjoy this immersive game for all types of players, inspired by the Japanese TV show <i>Hole in the Wall.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Introducing OhShape Ultimate!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy this celebrated VR rhythm game that offers a unique way of moving your whole body, a renewed look, and lots of extra content for this new era! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the c<strong>lassic wall-punching, obstacle-dodging, and fun pose-making</strong>, get your full-body cardio workout with 6 new sessions and 2 difficulty levels, with our <strong>Fitness Album</strong> designed to make you sweat and engage every part of your body! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into this fun-filled VR fitness album with OhShape by Odders Lab🤸 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/f57996fd27906bba0ae5eb52a7c85f99.avif?t=1742819123\" width=624 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OhShape is a rhythm game offering a unique way of moving your whole body. Dodge obstacles, punch walls, and make fun poses to get through each map. Play with the coins and be the star of your own show! Here are the features of OhShape Ultimate:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun poses and catchy music to keep you moving</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modern & dynamic looks and a much friendlier onboarding for new users.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun and great workout for your whole body</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A great gateway into the VR rhythm world but also a real challenge for the most seasoned players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 40 stages with 4 difficulty levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Electro Party DLC now for free</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party Mode: play and compete with your friends and family</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Practice Mode: Practice level sections to perfection!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom songs support with a very easy-to-use level editor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-platform online leaderboard<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump right into this new and fresh OhShape experience, and let us know your thoughts! <br><br><br> <br><br><strong>OhShape Level Editor </strong><br><strong> </strong><br>Here you can download the Level Editor. As it's open source, you can also download the code on GitHub.  <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/ac318b16be7ddfb6009719559a46764b.poster.avif?t=1742819123\" width=624 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/ac318b16be7ddfb6009719559a46764b.webm?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/ac318b16be7ddfb6009719559a46764b.mp4?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br>  <br>  Any questions? Check our FAQ!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OhShape F.A.Q.</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/2a7224d8e4bbc0969ce88c05fad2eb08.poster.avif?t=1742819123\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/2a7224d8e4bbc0969ce88c05fad2eb08.webm?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/2a7224d8e4bbc0969ce88c05fad2eb08.mp4?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OhShape is a rhythm VR game where players <strong>dance with their full body</strong> to go through, punch, and dodge walls following the beat of the music. Enjoy this immersive game for all types of players, inspired by the Japanese TV show <i>Hole in the Wall.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Introducing OhShape Ultimate!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy this celebrated VR rhythm game that offers a unique way of moving your whole body, a renewed look, and lots of extra content for this new era! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the c<strong>lassic wall-punching, obstacle-dodging, and fun pose-making</strong>, get your full-body cardio workout with 6 new sessions and 2 difficulty levels, with our <strong>Fitness Album</strong> designed to make you sweat and engage every part of your body! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into this fun-filled VR fitness album with OhShape by Odders Lab🤸 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/f57996fd27906bba0ae5eb52a7c85f99.avif?t=1742819123\" width=624 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OhShape is a rhythm game offering a unique way of moving your whole body. Dodge obstacles, punch walls, and make fun poses to get through each map. Play with the coins and be the star of your own show! Here are the features of OhShape Ultimate:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun poses and catchy music to keep you moving</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modern & dynamic looks and a much friendlier onboarding for new users.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fun and great workout for your whole body</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A great gateway into the VR rhythm world but also a real challenge for the most seasoned players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 40 stages with 4 difficulty levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Electro Party DLC now for free</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party Mode: play and compete with your friends and family</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Practice Mode: Practice level sections to perfection!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom songs support with a very easy-to-use level editor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross-platform online leaderboard<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump right into this new and fresh OhShape experience, and let us know your thoughts! <br><br><br> <br><br><strong>OhShape Level Editor </strong><br><strong> </strong><br>Here you can download the Level Editor. As it's open source, you can also download the code on GitHub.  <br>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/ac318b16be7ddfb6009719559a46764b.poster.avif?t=1742819123\" width=624 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/ac318b16be7ddfb6009719559a46764b.webm?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1098100/extras/ac318b16be7ddfb6009719559a46764b.mp4?t=1742819123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br>  <br>  Any questions? Check our FAQ!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>OhShape F.A.Q.</strong></p></li></ul>",
